'''[[Coma/Legends|Coma]] gas''' was a [[Color/Legends|colorless]], odorless gas used to incapacitate most [[Species/Legends|species]] of [[Humanoid/Legends|humanoids]]. Its use varied from riot control to full combat operations and saw widespread use throughout [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]]. Various forms of coma gas were used in [[boarding harpoon]]s by many [[Pirate/Legends|pirates]] and [[Privateer/Legends|privateer]] organizations, including the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]], who were intent on capturing vessels quickly and with a minimum of bloodshed. All it took was a few breaths of coma gas for a person to be out for hours.

During the [[Mission to Myrkr]], the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[Myrkr strike team|strike team]] used coma gas to facilitate their capture of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] [[I'Friil Ma-Nat|corvette analog]] ''[[Exquisite Death]]''.

